{"html": [{"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">AUTORIZA EMISORES ELECTR&#xD3;NICOS</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Extracto de resoluci&#xF3;n exenta del Servicio de Impuestos Internos N&#xBA; 112 de 29 de julio de 2009, que autoriza contribuyentes como emisor electr&#xF3;nico.</div></div>", "i": 8762024}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se autoriza como emisor de documentos tributarios electr&#xF3;nicos a contribuyentes RUT 78.035.640-5, RUT 77.199.330-3, RUT 76.201.390-8, RUT 76.049.664-2, RUT 70.372.500-7, RUT 96.671.320-8, RUT 76.028.333-9, RUT 96.919.980-7, RUT 96.981.310-6, RUT 90.413.000-1, RUT 78.986.340-7, RUT 76.009.700-4, RUT 76.498.260-6, RUT 76.486.860-9, RUT 76.220.150-K, RUT 96.937.420-K, RUT 78.954.120-5, RUT 76.369.370-8, RUT 96.599.680-K, RUT 96.568.950-8, RUT 87.161.100-9, RUT 96.999.910-2, RUT 76.857.990-3, RUT 76.554.400-9, RUT 96.563.290-5, RUT 86.150.200-7, RUT 77.753.800-4, RUT 77.008.610-8, RUT 72.173.800-0, RUT 76.930.710-9, RUT 76.924.610-K, RUT 86.304.100-7, RUT 59.108.900-5, RUT 78.517.090-3, RUT 77.355.160-K, RUT 76.016.027-K, RUT 10.672.943-3, RUT 76.883.170-K, RUT 06.554.967-0, RUT 77.910.940-2, RUT 76.718.230-9, RUT 96.941.080-K, RUT 76.023.515-6, RUT 76.056.215-7, RUT 96.684.040-4, RUT 79.506.430-3, RUT 76.736.010-K, RUT 77.806.960-1, RUT 76.558.030-7, RUT 79.880.550-9, RUT 76.041.579-0, RUT 77.035.820-5, RUT 99.502.420-9, RUT 79.794.890-K, RUT 76.109.190-5, RUT 76.218.020-0, RUT 80.914.400-3, RUT 77.556.090-8, RUT 76.058.390-1, RUT 76.022.944-K, RUT 76.969.500-1, RUT 76.801.700-K, RUT 79.702.920-3, RUT 83.156.400-8, RUT 96.989.480-7, RUT 96.797.560-5, RUT 99.508.950-5, RUT 79.862.750-3, RUT 96.969.180-9, RUT 79.713.460-0, RUT 99.531.920-9 y RUT 78.423.410-K a contar del mes de agosto 2009. En la Oficina Virtual del SII en Internet se podr&#xE1;n consultar los documentos que los contribuyentes est&#xE1;n autorizados a emitir en forma electr&#xF3;nica.</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  El texto &#xED;ntegr